-- Kevin Pietersen Is Added to England Squad for India Cricket Tour
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-10-18T14:26:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-18/kevin-pietersen-is-added-to-england-squad-for-india-cricket-tour.html
Kevin Pietersen  has been added to
England’s Test squad for the tour of India, the England 
and Wales Cricket Board said in a statement.  He was dropped from the third Test against South 
Africa in August after sending text messages to opposition
players. He’s also been in a wrangle with the cricket board over
his playing commitments.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  